import React, { Component } from 'react'
import Fullpage, { FullPageSections, FullpageSection } from '@ap.cx/react-fullpage'
import '../App.css';

export default class App extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Fullpage>

            <FullPageSections>

                <FullpageSection className="bg s1 section"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="bg s2 section"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="bg s3 section"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="bg s4 section"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="bg s5 section"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="bg s6 section"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="bg s7 section"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="bg s8 section"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="bg s9"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="bg s10"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="bg s11"></FullpageSection>
                

            </FullPageSections>

        </Fullpage>
        )
    }
}
